Title: BPS Conditions of Supermembrane on the PP-wave
Authors: Katsuyuki Sugiyama and Kentaroh Yoshida (Kyoto Univ.)
Comments: 13 pages, no figures, LaTeX, (v2),(v3);typos corrected
Report-no: KUCP-0212
Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B546 (2002) 143-152
\\
  We study the BPS conditions in the closed supermembranes on the maximally
supersymmetric pp-wave background. In particular, the 1/2 and 1/4 BPS states
are discussed in detail. Moreover, we comment on the zero-modes in the
invariant mass formulae of the theory.
